headline: Why Williams-Sonoma (WSM) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of kitchenware and home goods retailer Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) jumped 3.2% in the afternoon session after the company’s Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.66 per share.
